      "content": "hey i need some help with a trip. im flying into heathrow and need to get up to edinburgh. im thinking of taking the heathrow express to paddington then catching an LNER train from kings cross and then a bus once i get there. whats a good amount of buffer time i should leave between the heathrow express and the LNER train just in case of delays?",
